abstract: "PromptDC for VS Code is a coding-first prompt enhancer, optimizer, and rewriter that transforms vague developer prompts into precise, implementation-ready instructions optimized for AI code generation across Copilot, Cline, Claude Code, Gemini, Codex, Kilo Code, and all major LLMs. BYOK Lifetime from $69; Pro $9/mo; no free plan."
